com.opengamma.strata.calc.marketdata

Class DefaultCalculationMarketData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.calc.marketdata.DefaultCalculationMarketData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CalculationMarketData

    public final class DefaultCalculationMarketData
extends Object
implements CalculationMarketData
    A source of market data used for a calculation across multiple scenarios.

    This implementation is backed by a CalculationEnvironment and MarketDataMappings. Methods on this interface take a key. The mappings are used to resolve the key into the ID necessary to query CalculationEnvironment.

        public LocalDateDoubleTimeSeries getTimeSeries(ObservableKey key)
        Description copied from interface: CalculationMarketData
        Gets the time-series identified by the specified key, empty if not found.

        Time series are not affected by scenarios, therefore there is a single time-series for each key which is shared between all scenarios.
